---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="KI-Implementierung - Synclaro" description="Professionelle KI-Implementierung für Ihr Unternehmen. Von der Strategie bis zum Go-Live. 6 Wochen Express. 100% DSGVO-konform. ROI-Garantie.">

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 px-4 md:px-8 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-swiss-orange font-bold text-lg mb-4">KI-IMPLEMENTIERUNG</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
          <span class="text-swiss-orange">KI-Implementierung</span> die funktioniert
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-3xl">
          Von der Strategie bis zum Go-Live: Wir implementieren KI-Lösungen, die nahtlos in Ihre bestehenden Prozesse integriert werden und vom ersten Tag an Mehrwert schaffen.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/lp/express-configurator" class="inline-block bg-swiss-orange text-white px-8 py-4 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-black transition-colors duration-300 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
            Implementierung planen
          </a>
          <a href="https://cal.com/marcoheer/erstgesprach" class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-8 py-4 font-bold text-lg border-2 border-black hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors duration-300">
            Beratungsgespräch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Implementation Process -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 md:px-8 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6">
          Der <span class="text-swiss-orange">Implementierungsprozess</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Phase 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Phase 1: Analyse & Strategie</h3>
            <span class="text-swiss-orange font-bold text-lg">1-2 Wochen</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Ist-Analyse Ihrer Prozesse</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Identifikation von KI-Potenzialen</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Technische Machbarkeitsprüfung</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">ROI-Berechnung und Business Case</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Phase 2: Konzeption & Design</h3>
            <span class="text-swiss-orange font-bold text-lg">2-3 Wochen</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Lösungsarchitektur entwickeln</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Datenmodelle definieren</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Integrationskonzept erstellen</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">UI/UX Design der Lösung</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Phase 3: Entwicklung & Integration</h3>
            <span class="text-swiss-orange font-bold text-lg">4-8 Wochen</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">KI-Modelle trainieren</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">APIs entwickeln</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">System-Integration</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Testing & Qualitätssicherung</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Phase 4: Rollout & Optimierung</h3>
            <span class="text-swiss-orange font-bold text-lg">2-4 Wochen</span>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Pilotphase mit Kernteam</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Mitarbeiterschulung</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Go-Live und Monitoring</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-swiss-orange mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Kontinuierliche Optimierung</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technologies Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 md:px-8 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6">
          Modernste <span class="text-swiss-orange">Technologien</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- KI-Modelle -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-swiss-orange flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4">KI-Modelle</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <p>GPT-4 & Claude</p>
            <p>Custom Fine-Tuning</p>
            <p>RAG-Systeme</p>
            <p>Computer Vision</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Integrationen -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-swiss-orange flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4">Integrationen</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <p>REST & GraphQL APIs</p>
            <p>Webhooks</p>
            <p>Event Streaming</p>
            <p>ETL Pipelines</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Infrastruktur -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-swiss-orange flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-2-4h.01M17 16h.01"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-4">Infrastruktur</h3>
          <div class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <p>Cloud & On-Premise</p>
            <p>Kubernetes</p>
            <p>Auto-Scaling</p>
            <p>24/7 Monitoring</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 md:px-8 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6">
          <span class="text-swiss-orange">Häufige Fragen</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-3">Wie lange dauert eine KI-Implementierung?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Die Dauer hängt vom Umfang ab. Ein MVP ist in 6-8 Wochen möglich, eine vollständige Implementierung dauert typischerweise 3-6 Monate.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-3">Welche Systeme können integriert werden?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Wir integrieren alle gängigen Systeme: CRM (Salesforce, HubSpot), ERP (SAP, Microsoft Dynamics), Office 365, Google Workspace und viele mehr.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-3">Was kostet eine KI-Implementierung?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Die Kosten beginnen bei 15.000€ für unser Essential-Paket. Gerne erstellen wir Ihnen ein individuelles Angebot basierend auf Ihren Anforderungen.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-3">Wie sicher sind unsere Daten?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Datensicherheit hat höchste Priorität. Wir arbeiten 100% DSGVO-konform, bieten On-Premise-Lösungen und verschlüsseln alle Daten nach höchsten Standards.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4 md:px-8 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black mb-6">
        Starten Sie Ihre KI-Transformation
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8">
        In 6 Wochen von der Idee zur produktiven KI-Lösung
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/lp/express-configurator" class="inline-block bg-swiss-orange text-white px-8 py-4 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300 shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(255,79,0,1)]">
          Jetzt starten
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+4916099471052" class="inline-block bg-transparent text-white px-8 py-4 font-bold text-lg border-2 border-white hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300">
          0160 99471052
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
